ent and safe","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpeak what is good and acquire gains, or refrain from speaking evil and be safe.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Shihab al-Qud\u0323a\u0304\u02bbi\u0304 666 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u062a\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11864,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/29\/speechh-haqq-silence-safe\/","url_meta":{"origin":20475,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Silence: Speak truth, or be silent and safe","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on a man who spoke rightly and was rewarded, or who was silent and remained safe.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 4589 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21687,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/19\/allah-silent-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":20475,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Silence: Allah is silent on matters for your benefit","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat Allah has made lawful in his book is lawful, and what he has made unlawful is unlawful. Whatever he has remained silent upon, it is for your benefit, so accept benefit from Allah. Verily, Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32825,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/17\/safe-as-long-as-silent\/","url_meta":{"origin":20475,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Silence: You are safe as long as you stay silent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, you will continue to be safe as long as you remain silent. If you speak, it will be recorded for you or against you.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kab\u012br lil-\u1e6cabar\u0101n\u012b 20\/73 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20401,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/02\/21\/character-silent-mindfulness\/","url_meta":{"origin":20475,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Allah loves good character, silent reflection","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, met Abu Dharr and he said, \u201cO Abu Dharr, shall I not tell you of two qualities that are easy on your back and heavier on the scale of good than others?\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cOf course, O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11985,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/02\/most-sins-lisan-kalam\/","url_meta":{"origin":20475,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Speech: Most sins committed by the tongue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMost of the sins of the children of Adam are on their tongues.\u201d Ibn Mas'ud said, \"O tongue! Speak goodness and be rewarded, or remain silent and be safe, lest you become regretful.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/20475","targetHints":{"allow":["